From jari.oksanen at oulu.fi  Wed Aug 18 10:14:16 2010
From: jari.oksanen at oulu.fi (Jari Oksanen)
Date: Wed, 18 Aug 2010 11:14:16 +0300
Subject: [R-sig-eco] pearson correlation with axes of NMDS or capscale
In-Reply-To: <D023402611CE1546BD7E9CB8A002A32201534D30@xmail02.ad.ua.ac.be>
